  style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #34495e 0%, #2c3e50 100%); color: white; padding: 
  40px 20px; text-align: center;"><h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 2.5em; font-weight: normal; 
  letter-spacing: 2px;">Daily Benedictine Reflection</h1></div><div style="background-color: 
